parameters.name: PDSTIME
parameters.description:
Spacecraft event time of the sample.               
        The time string is of the form YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sss.               
        The representation of Jan 01, 2000, 00:00:00.000 would be             
        2000-01-01T00:00:00.000.

parameters.name: SPACECRAFT_CLOCK
parameters.description:
Spacecraft clock counter frame and minor           
        frame (mod91) counters in the form  frame:mf

parameters.name: M_STEP
parameters.description:
M/Q analyzer step (0-63). Nonzero only for mass    
                           spectrometer detectors.

parameters.name: SECTOR_ID
parameters.description:
AACS sector (clock angle) at start of spin-sector  
                           (0-255). In some instances, this value is greater  
                           than 255.  These instance might be errors but      
                           can't be corrected at this time.

parameters.name: SAMPLE_NO
parameters.description:
Sequential sample number in spin-block.            
                           First sample is 1,last sample is                   
                           (number-of-steps)*(number-of-sectors).
